d125 5
a129 3
			<code>option: &nbsp; ressource: &nbsp; signification </code> <br>
			&nbsp;<code>-fa  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *faceName</code> &nbsp;&nbsp; Nom de la police <br>
			&nbsp;<code>-fs  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *faceSize</code> &nbsp;&nbsp; Taille de la police <br>
